    {
      "id": "90",
      "name": "Média",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Trailers & Teasers",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Aperçu de l'histoire : « Les Yakshas, gardiens Adeptes »",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/23/237301566/90f7b599b4d7f65c3edf3844d9cf3f04_5140932463371261091.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "27/01/2021",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Alatus, Roi aux Ailes d'Or, Dompteur de démons. De son origine comme de sa fin nul n'a connaissance.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Seulement lors de l'offrande des lanternes à la nuit de printemps, son éclat domine les pierres de Guyun. Alors le peuple dit :",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "« Oyez, le Gardien Yaksha terrasse les démons ».",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Alors des marais retentit la flûte, mais nul n'est vu en jouer. Et le peuple dit : « Ses frères le Yaksha appelle. »",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube :",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Aperçu de l'histoire : « Seuls les vieux souvenirs restent »",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/23/237301566/68227850eb221e54dc2b6c91f89e1436_291937187263281196.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "02/06/2022",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Une fois hors de danger, tous se dispersent, pensifs ou satisfaits.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Seul Xiao reste pour vous conter le souvenir passé d'un Yaksha...",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube :",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Aperçu de l'histoire : « Son persistant »",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/23/237301566/083477d4fe3e4626f8d54ba962d5cae2_4419010495052526109.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "21/01/2023",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Les nuages brumeux fuient lentement, les nénuphars flottent au gré de l'eau.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "L'eau qui coule doucement emporte avec elle toutes les poussières.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube :",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
